{"tid":1024030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國拒收的洋垃圾讓馬來西亞小鎮窒息 E-mail 此主題給朋友","createTime":"2019-02-16T08:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T12:12:03.000Z","uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dcf91b137229ef2b60429e2dfa0e020a5b2d7ffd","tid":1024030,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:46:31.000Z","msg":"中國決定禁止進口洋垃圾後，主要來自美國、日本和英國的廢棄塑料就被運往了新的目的地 － 馬來西亞。僅僅從2018年1月到7月，就有75.4萬噸塑料垃圾進口到馬來西亞。一些被當地政府視為非法的塑料回收工廠也應運而生，希圖在價值7.34億美元的巨額塑料回收業中牟取暴利。<br />\n根據當地州政府統計，在仁嘉隆鎮所在的瓜拉冷月縣（Kuala Langat）就有33座非法回收工廠。有些靠近生產棕櫚油的植物園，有些靠近城市。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/684eb5/f/800x0/https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/1024x576/p071070r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F684eb5%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fimages%2Fic%2F1024x576%2Fp071070r.jpg&h=81691f3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國人害人不淺<br />\n<br />\n馬拉人民抗議<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-47243267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-47243267&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=a0b96adb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-47243267&h=50bb8f89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-47243267</a>"},{"pid":"24fc1cd4906e80f143572699fd49e377e9fcd7df","tid":1024030,"uid":14103,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:15:48.000Z","msg":"支那原來有進口垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢自己本身都係一舊垃圾"},{"pid":"cb2253eb369c94f838215348271947f5dfd8d40d","tid":1024030,"uid":46245,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:25:01.000Z","msg":"老實講支那又無錯，無人會想要垃圾，除非回收有錢賺（膠類、玻璃類多數倒貼做），發達國家英美日唔要唔代表支那就要承受既"},{"pid":"f48be523bb5fabc412ec880599f241ec4b3275a4","tid":1024030,"uid":181294,"like":2,"dislike"